overview.overview: Jitsi Meet - Secure, Simple and Scalable Video Conferences that you use as a standalone app or embed in your web application.

childMarkdownRemark.html:
Jitsi Meet is a set of Open Source projects which empower users to use and deploy video conferencing platforms with state-of-the-art video quality and features.

Amongst others here are the main features Jitsi Meet offers:

  • Support for all current browsers
  • Mobile applications
  • Web and native SDKs for integration
  • HD audio and video
  • Content sharing
  • Raise hand and reactions
  • Chat with private conversations
  • Polls
  • Virtual backgrounds
